1536.831&#x02005;nm, in air at 298&#x02005;K</td><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">measured</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">1525.456&#x02005;nm, in LHe at 2.168&#x02005;K</td><td>&#x000a0;</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">1525.429&#x02005;nm, in LHe at 2.000&#x02005;K</td><td>&#x000a0;</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">Disk's radiation quality factor (<italic>Q</italic><sub>v</sub>)</td><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">2.33 &#x000d7; 10<sup>5</sup>, in air at 298&#x02005;K</td><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">measured</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">4.04 &#x000d7; 10<sup>5</sup>, in LHe at 2.168&#x02005;K</td><td>&#x000a0;</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">4.89 &#x000d7; 10<sup>5</sup>, in LHe at 2.000&#x02005;K</td><td>&#x000a0;</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">Disk's coupling quality factor (<italic>Q</italic><sub>in</sub>)</td><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">2.10 &#x000d7; 10<sup>6</sup>, in air at 298&#x02005;K</td><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">measured</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">2.15 &#x000d7; 10<sup>6</sup>, in LHe at 2.168&#x02005;K</td><td>&#x000a0;</td></tr><tr><td align="justify" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">2.20 &#x000d7; 10<sup>6</sup>, in LHe at 2.000&#x02005;K</td><td>&#x000a0;</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap></floats-group></article>